<p>[picture of Gallipoli. Annotated as follows :-]<br/>Lone Pine is away about two miles and under the arrow<br/>Note the steam pinnace<br/>And this bit of rough jetty is where I landed 17.5.15</p>
<p>The path over Hell Spit is plainly seen. It was on that path where saw the man blown to pieces when I was first there</p>
<p>[Page 20]<br/>[Back of Gallipoli picture ]<br/>Anzac cove from the north showing Hells Spit (mentioned in my letters)<br/>In the distance marked x is Gaba Tepe note the lighters and also Watson Pier with lighter near it<br/>Arthur</p>
